────────────────────────────────────────
SECTION 1 — OVERVIEW
────────────────────────────────────────
A ride sharing app that connects riders
with drivers. Riders can book trips and
track their driver. Drivers can accept
multiple riders in one trip.

Scope
─────────────────
Included
- Rider booking and tracking
- Driver trip management
- Ratings
- Trip history

Not Included
- Payments
- Admin dashboard
- Scheduling future trips


────────────────────────────────────────
SECTION 2 — USER ROLES
────────────────────────────────────────
Rider
─────────────────
- Books trips
- Tracks driver
- Rates driver after trip

Driver
─────────────────
- Accepts riders
- Manages active trip
- Rates riders after trip


────────────────────────────────────────
SECTION 3 — FUNCTIONS
────────────────────────────────────────

── RIDER ──────────────────────────────

FUNCTION: Register
─────────────────
Actor       Rider
Trigger     Rider submits registration form
Input       firstName, lastName, phoneNumber, email
Process     Create rider account
Output      Rider id
Result      Rider account created

FUNCTION: Login
─────────────────
Actor       Rider
Trigger     Rider submits login form
Input       email, phoneNumber
Process     Verify rider account
Output      Auth token
Result      Rider logged in

FUNCTION: Book a Trip
─────────────────
Actor       Rider
Trigger     Rider submits booking request
Input       riderId, starting_location, ending_location
Process     Find available driver
            Calculate price
            Create active booking
Output      tripId, driverId, price
Result      Booking created
            Driver notified

FUNCTION: Cancel a Trip
─────────────────
Actor       Rider
Trigger     Rider cancels before inVan
Input       tripId, riderId
Process     Remove rider from active booking
Output      Confirmation
Result      Booking cancelled
            Driver notified

FUNCTION: View Active Booking
─────────────────
Actor       Rider
Trigger     Rider opens active booking screen
Input       riderId
Process     Fetch active booking record
Output      tripId, driverId, status, price,
            starting_location, ending_location,
            current_locationDriver
Result      Rider sees current trip details

FUNCTION: Update Own Location
─────────────────
Actor       Rider
Trigger     Rider location changes
Input       riderId, current_locationRider
